{"tid":877551,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"二手成交：東環三房套勁減18%沽","createTime":"2018-10-26T12:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T14:34:19.000Z","uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6b40eb22115e8dcca19a85cddf6e2f36995826ba","tid":877551,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181026/photo/bkn-20181026152804801-1026_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181026162145\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181026152804801-1026_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181026162145&h=c3149b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利嘉閣地產皇牌屋苑藍天海岸一行高級經理劉景駿表示，市場新近錄得東涌東環2期1A座低層7室的二手成交個案，實用面積約587方呎，採三房一套連開放式廚房設計，外望泳池景觀。單位於九月時叫價840萬港元放售，及後減價150萬元或約18%，以690萬元獲承接，折合實用面積呎價約11,755元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主於2015年10月，以約609.6萬元購入上述單位。SSD鬆綁，現轉手帳面獲利約80.4萬元，物業價值升幅約13%。<br />\n<br />\n東環本月暫錄約4宗成交個案，平均實用面積呎價約13,500元。屋苑前約有150個單位放售，「入場費」由約570萬元起。"},{"pid":"12d8a642db9a93e21b26e53c7200f5e388fead29","tid":877551,"uid":73598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"三年前買都幾乎蟹，呢兩年先買既會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d269fae135d2d8c9d560726f49272294356554","tid":877551,"uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/201813_4c3ade940ab50d9fc1c49d9370b16ee6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F201813_4c3ade940ab50d9fc1c49d9370b16ee6.png&h=34ee43b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd5678b5a65a4987a51d9cc85ab557f7e678c3da","tid":877551,"uid":112720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23d269fae135d2d8c9d560726f49272294356554","tid":877551,"uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src